# Build

## From source

To generate the configure script and Makefile with m4, run

	./bootstrap

Then build as if from release.

## From release

To configure astral-box, run

	./configure [option]...

For options, run

	./configure --help

To build astral-box, run

	make

# Test

To run all of the tests, run

	make check

To run the tests for a specific <util>, run

	make check-<util>

# Install

To install astral-box, run

	make install
